    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine, original condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a complete service history. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that requires absolutely nothing but a new owner.",
